loss rules governing what officers and enlisted personnel may be 
kept on in the service even if they are ready to retire or their 
enlistment has expired and they dont want to sign up again 
there are policy changes under consideration army 
spokeswoman judy johnston said thursday 
and one pentagon official speaking on the condition of 
anonymity said an announcement on the subject was being prepared 
