a man who was imprisoned for nearly five 
years under a false name even though authorities suspected he was 
lying about his identity was finally tripped up by an offhand 
reference to hawaii authorities said 
authorities didnt know much about the man who was sentenced as 
joseph p caldwell in early 1986 in pierce county superior court 
because his history was a blank he received a lighter sentence 
than he might have if is criminal past had been known 
