economic and political affairs the situation in the country 
continues to worsen and is approaching a crisis condition it 
said 
another resolution passed recommended that gorbachev take all 
steps authorized by law up to extraordinary measures in cases 
where there is a threat to human life health or property 
that measure removed a requirement for the president to consult 
with leaders of the republics before taking such measures and gave 
