dictatorship an attempt to go for the jugular to take 
advantage of the situation opponents he said really want to 
let the paralysis of power continue 
gorbachevs proposals to restructure the government are aimed at 
ridding the power structure of officials resistant to radical 
reform and bringing in representatives of the republics 
todays resolution also endorsed gorbachevs proposal to 
eliminate the council of ministers or soviet cabinet and make 
another body the highest state organ that proposal has a number of 
other legislative hurdles before it becomes law 
the lawmakers told the president today to submit more concrete 
definitions of what each new government body would do within two 
weeks 
under the outline the council of ministers would be replaced by 
several bodies under direct presidential control the principal 
ruling body would be the federation council grouping 
representatives of the republics 
many of gorbachevs proposals will require constitutional 
amendments which must be adopted by the supreme soviets parent 
body the congress of peoples deputies 
