he complained weve starved to keep the horses we survived 
the civil war the 1982 israeli invasion and aouns wars hoping 
against all odds to race again with peace in sight now the 
government says no its not fair 
the track was inaugurated in 1916 under the ottoman empire the 
present governing committee took an 80year lease for the grounds 
in 1920 when france ruled lebanon after world war i 
