known as eni 
eni already owns 40 percent of enimont its bid to buy 
montedisons 40 percent stake and increase its holding to a 
controlling 80 percent ended a bitter 18month battle between 
gardini and eni officials 
eni also offered to buy out minority shareholders to take 
complete control of enimont 
