ferruzzi finanziaria the key holding company of the 
agroindustrial and chemical groups of the ferruzzi family 
a statement said gardini was leaving for ideological reasons 
and would no longer participate in any italian company or 
business organization 
eni and montedison formed enimont in 1989 in an effort to 
restructure italys chemical industry creating the worlds 10th 
largest chemical group with annual revenue of about 136 billion 
