the moves are a clear signal the nations economy is slowing down 
a spokeswoman for germanys volkswagen ag spanish subsidiary 
seat sa said thursday that the company will cut production by 120 
cars a day and lay off 700 temporary workers because of a sharp 
decline in sales in spain this year 
 
